These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, cain, tiparillo, montecristo
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, dancing, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, dancer, entrepreneur, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, superhero, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, techno, trance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, lily, poppy
4 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, turtle, rat
 1. the bongani-smoker is the person watching action movies##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
 4. the dancer is on the far right##1
 5. the dancer is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the owner of the hamster is the cain-smoker##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the owner of the rat is the fan of salsa##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the chef##1
11. the person who growssunflower is the cain-smoker##1
12. the owner of the mouse is the fan of techno##1
13. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
14. the person who growstulip is the montecristo-smoker##1
15. the person who growspoppy is the entrepreneur##1
16. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the chef##1
17. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | bongani       | montecristo      | tiparillo       | cain    |
| Hobby         | board-games    | puzzles    | cooking      | dancing    |
| Job           | security-guard | chef       | entrepreneur | dancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | action         | superhero  | western      | comedy     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa          | trance     | techno       | electronic |
| Flower         | lily       | tulip | poppy       | sunflower   |
| Pet     | rat     | turtle  | mouse         | hamster   |

